{"tid":1908710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"休班警駕電單車大埔撼欄　拋飛10米傷重亡","createTime":"2020-03-03T12:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T13:02:59.000Z","uid":181703,"like":20,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"55660f1ea805084a81dc503f40b48d89198590e8","tid":1908710,"uid":181703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"大埔有休班警駕鐵騎「自炒」喪命。昨日（2日）晚上11時許，休班男警黃卓華（33歲），駕乘本田CB1000R大馬力電單車，沿大埔太和路支路往吐露港公路北行，途經一個右彎位時，懷疑失控猛撞向路旁防撞欄，由於衝力猛烈，黃登時人車分離，被拋至10米欄外倒地，頭部重創浴血，電單車繼續向前滑行翻側。有其他駕駛者見狀，即時落車察看，同時協助報警。 <br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料，肇事電單車於2011年出廠，同年4月由一名姓黃男子首次登記，當年車價逾11萬港元，車主報住屯門美樂花園。 <br />\n<br />\n搵到錢都冇命享呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/mobile/bkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001.html&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVppgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=3686b7d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/mobile/bkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/photo/bkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190304174708\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190303002416327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190304174708&h=7962406d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba57df18407757d8d6bc3b7728844ced1d554a9d","tid":1908710,"uid":51234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"Fake. Old news"},{"pid":"189095c0f9c05050645458ff7a198930bbdc86d8","tid":1908710,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img sr